ting mode available in New Game+<br></li><li> Steam Achievements!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942580/extras/561290c6e30d659066842c24da67065a.webp?t=1659890965\" width=532 height=43 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942580/extras/63604cd56318e007c24f878950487a23.avif?t=1659890965\" width=512 height=588 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942580/extras/9487c5a665c5a1bd5eb9204ecd2bce8a.avif?t=1659890965\" width=512 height=588 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942580/extras/44a389155dedc2964cb147b90c438de6.avif?t=1659890965\" width=512 height=588 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942580/extras/779d01a8ab1ffc6c31ca90aa41b235d6.avif?t=1659890965\" width=512 height=588 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942580/extras/385641aaf0a34f72412d334bfa22bd7c.avif?t=1659890965\" width=512 height=588 /></span><br><strong><i>....and many, many more!</i></strong>",
